txt.en: You have not yet slain enough Orcs.

Orcs of the White Mountains can be found in Gurz-shâpol to the north of Dunharrow.\n\nYou have discovered a cave filled with vicious Orcs poised to strike against the Rohirrim. You should defeat many of their number.
You have discovered a cave filled with vicious Orcs poised to strike against the Rohirrim. You should defeat many of their number.
You have defeated a great many Rashat-hai Orcs in Gurz-shâpol.
The Orcs of the White Mountains have long harried the Rohirrim, and through your efforts, you have protected Underharrow and Edoras from their impending assault.
From their settlement in Gurz-shâpol, the ghastly Rashat-hai of the White Mountains raid the Harrowdale, striking fear into the hearts of the Rohirrim.

You have discovered an expansive cave teeming with Orcs under the White Mountains.  Their numbers are great, and should they remain unchecked, the Orcs could easily overwhelm the defenceless at Underharrow. For the safety of the Harrowdale and Edoras itself, the Orcs must be defeated.
